- [ ] `test_semaphore_fifo_different_counts` - A requests 2, B requests 1, A should get first
- [ ] `test_semaphore_no_queue_jump` - New arrival doesn't bypass waiting task
- [ ] `test_semaphore_partial_available` - Partial permits don't enable jumping
- [ ] `test_semaphore_release_wakes_first` - Release wakes front of queue
